title: Hue Jackson Fired, Browns coaching candidates
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn for an emergency podcast after the Browns fired Hue Jackson and Todd Haley. What's the fallout in Cleveland? Who are the likely candidates up next for the Browns? Plus, did the Bucs make the right decision going with Ryan Fitzpatrick and what will happen to Jameis Winston? All that and much more.
